eading to the consistent dropping of the initial <i>H-</i> and to her representation in art accompanied by a lamb. The colloquial form <i>Annes</i> led to some confusion with <i>Ann(e)</i> in earlier centuries. Frequent in the medieval period, the name was revived in the 19th century, and has been especially popular in Scotland.  See also  Annis ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Agnes Burgloin was born in 1397, in Downton, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 son with John Bishop Iii. She died in 1440, at the age of 43."},"et":{"1397–1440":"1397–1440","1397–1470":"1397–1470","1420–1470":"1420–1470","1420":"1420","1397":"1397","1440":"1440","1470":"1470","Downton, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom":"Downton, Wiltshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1397–1440":"1397–1440","1397–1470":"1397–1470","1420–1470":"1420–1470","1420":"1420","1397":"1397","1440":"1440","1470":"1470","Downton, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom":"Downton, Wiltshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1397–1440":"1397–1440","1397–1470":"1397–1470","1420–1470":"1420–1470","1420":"1420","1397":"1397","1440":"1440","1470":"1470","Downton, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom":"Downton, Wiltshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Agnes Burgloin est née en 1397, à Downton, Wiltshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec John Bishop Iii. Elle est décédée en 1440, à l’âge de 43 ans."},"de":{"1397–1440":"1397–1440","1397–1470":"1397–1470","1420–1470":"1420–1470","1420":"1420","1397":"1397","1440":"1440","1470":"1470","Downton, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom":"Downton, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Agnes Burgloin wurde 1397 in Downton, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom geboren. Sie hatte mit John Bishop Iii mindestens 1 Sohn. Sie starb 1440 im Alter von 43 Jahren."},"ht":{"1397–1440":"1397–1440","1397–1470":"1397–1470","1420–1470":"1420–1470","1420":"1420","1397":"1397","1440":"1440","1470":"1470","Downton, Wiltshire, Eng